title: The Hollow Hope - Rosenberg 2nd Edition.pdf
description:
This book challenged the assumption that courts can and have produced social change. The second edition responds to the developments around Same-Sex Marriage in the court system before 2008. It should be noted that the 2 landmark rulings United States V. Windsor (2013), and Obergefell V. Hodges (2015). He responds to the 2004 state supreme court ruling, however the larger picture wasn't revealed to him in 2008.

9780226726717 - Gerald N. Rosenberg
